    <item>
      <title>喀麦隆债券因投资者权衡政治稳定风险而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/cameroon-bonds-drop-as-investors-weigh-political-stability-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对该国总统健康状况的猜测引发了人们对潜在继任之争的担忧，喀麦隆美元债券连续第三天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/cameroon-bonds-drop-as-investors-weigh-political-stability-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗氏首席执行官称将加大在华生产以满足本地市场需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/pharma-giant-roche-will-make-more-drugs-diagnostic-products-in-china-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗氏控股公司将在中国增加生产能力，以服务中国不断增长的市场，成为中美贸易竞争加剧背景下最新一家分拆部分生产的制药巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/pharma-giant-roche-will-make-more-drugs-diagnostic-products-in-china-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:49:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>央行调查显示印度通胀预期正在缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/india-s-inflation-expectations-easing-central-bank-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行最新的季度调查显示，家庭通胀预期有所缓解，这给政策制定者提供了考虑降息的进一步理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/india-s-inflation-expectations-easing-central-bank-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Exane 因供应过剩削减石油巨头股票评级，埃克森美孚股价罕见下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/exxon-gets-rare-sell-as-exane-cuts-oil-majors-on-oversupply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预计原油价格将进一步下跌，法国巴黎银行证券部分析师下调了三大石油公司的评级，埃克森美孚公司获得了一年多来首次卖出评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/exxon-gets-rare-sell-as-exane-cuts-oil-majors-on-oversupply</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:49:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冬季需求逼近 英国天然气价格超过欧洲基准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-gas-futures-outrun-europe-benchmark-on-looming-winter-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国天然气期货价格已高于欧洲大陆的基准合约，这表明交易商开始为需求增长做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-gas-futures-outrun-europe-benchmark-on-looming-winter-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:44:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刺激计划疑虑导致中国股市创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员对北京方面刺激措施的步伐感到不耐烦，且疲软的假日消费数据打击了市场人气，中国在岸上市的股票遭遇了四年多来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:35:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价下跌，因美国原油库存增加，交易员担心中国刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价下跌，延续了前一交易日的大幅跌势，因为交易商准备应对美国原油库存的大幅增加，并关注中国的财政政策计划以及中东局势的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 23:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要和 CPI 公布前，股市涨势停滞：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待美联储最新政策会议纪要和关键通胀数据，以寻找央行下一步行动的线索，股市难以获得太大的上涨空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 22:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
